item.title: Hidden Truths in Human Design - A Conversation with Trish Murray
item.description: In today’s episode, we meet Trish Murray who shares how we can better understand ourselves by exploring our human design, which is like our personal blueprint. That blueprint can then be used to amplify our life “360 degrees” and create well-being and balance. We touch on numerology, birth data, soul styles, and living in the Age of Aquarius - all information we can use to better understand who we are... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/joyful-journey/
